    Real Estate Scraper Tool Extract Property Leads

    Created by the owner of the listed website. The publisher has a good record with no history of violations. Learn more.
    https://www.scrappertool.com/
    ExtensionTools40 users

    Overview

    Real estate scraper tool to extract property leads from popular Real Estate platforms.

    Real Estate Scraper Tool Extract Property Leads Real Estate Scraper Tool Extract Property Leads is a Chrome extension built to scrape property listings and collect real estate data from popular property listing websites. It helps users extract structured property information and property leads without manual copy-paste work. This tool is useful for anyone who works with property listings, housing data, or real estate leads and wants a simple way to collect publicly available property information. If you are searching for a real estate scraper tool, property scraper tool, housing scraper tool, or a website-specific scraper like Housing, 99acres, MagicBricks, Airbnb, or Zillow, this extension is designed for those use cases. Supported Property Listing Websites The Real Estate Scraper Tool works with publicly available listings from: Housing 99acres MagicBricks Airbnb Zillow The tool can scrape property data from search result pages and individual listing pages without depending on a fixed page layout. Property Scraper Tool What Data Can Be Extracted This property scraper tool allows you to extract important real estate data such as: Property title Property type Price Area or size Location and address Agent or owner name if publicly visible Property listing URL Property images You can choose only the fields you need and export the data in a clean format. Housing Scraper Tool Scrape Housing Data The Housing scraper tool feature helps users scrape housing data from Housing property listings. With this tool, you can: Scrape housing property listings Extract price, area, and location details Collect housing property URLs Export housing data for analysis or lead generation This is useful for users looking to scrape housing data for market research, sales outreach, or property comparison. 99acres Scraping Tool Extract Property Listings The Real Estate Scraper Tool also works as a 99acres scraping tool. You can: Scrape 99acres property listings Extract property prices and locations Collect listing URLs and images Export 99acres property data in CSV or Excel format This makes it suitable for users searching for a 99acres property scraper or a tool to extract real estate data from Indian property websites. MagicBricks Scraper Tool Collect Property Data This extension can be used as a MagicBricks scraper tool to extract publicly available property listings. You can: Scrape MagicBricks property listings Extract pricing and address details Collect structured real estate data Export MagicBricks property data for further use It is helpful for users who want to analyze MagicBricks listings or collect property data for business use. Airbnb Scraper Tool Extract Listing Information The Real Estate Scraper Tool also supports Airbnb property listings. Using this Airbnb scraper tool, you can: Scrape Airbnb listing data Extract property titles and locations Collect listing URLs and images Export Airbnb data for analysis This is useful for users working with short-term rental data, property research, or listing comparison. Zillow Scraper Tool Scrape Zillow Property Data This extension works as a Zillow scraper tool for scraping publicly available Zillow property listings. You can: Scrape Zillow property listings Extract prices, locations, and property details Collect Zillow listing URLs Export Zillow property data for research or analysis If someone searches for a Zillow scraper tool or a way to scrape Zillow data using a Chrome extension, this tool matches that intent. Automated Real Estate Data Scraping This real estate scraper tool automates the process of collecting property listings. Users can: Scrape multiple property listings at once Extract real estate leads efficiently Reduce manual work Save time on repetitive tasks The tool is lightweight and suitable for regular use. Easy to Use Interface The extension is designed for simplicity. No technical skills required Clean and easy interface Quick setup and fast results Anyone can start scraping property listings within minutes. Export Property Data Scraped property data can be exported in multiple formats: CSV Excel JSON This makes it easy to use the data in CRM systems, spreadsheets, or analysis tools. Who Can Use This Real Estate Scraper Tool This tool is suitable for: Real estate agents and brokers Property consultants Marketing and lead generation teams Data researchers and analysts Businesses working with property listings If you work with property data or real estate leads, this tool can simplify your workflow. Privacy and Safe Usage Scrapes only publicly available web data Does not bypass logins or paywalls All data is processed locally in your browser No data is collected, stored, or shared User privacy is always respected. Support For any questions or issues related to the Real Estate Scraper Tool, contact: info.scrappertool@gmail.com Disclaimer This Chrome extension is not endorsed, certified, or affiliated with Housing, 99acres, MagicBricks, Airbnb, Zillow, or any other real estate platform. It is an independent property data extraction tool. Privacy Policy https://www.scrappertool.com/privacy-policy.html Legal Notice All trademarks and brand names belong to their respective owners and are used only for identification purposes. This is an independent project developed by SCRAPPERTOOL.
